config PINCTRL_SUN8I_V3S
    bool "Allwinner SUN8I v3s SoC pin controller driver"
    default y
    depends on DT_HAS_ALLWINNER_SUN8I_V3S_PINCTRL_ENABLED
    help
      Allwinner SUN8I v3s SoC pin controller driver.
      Manages its own PIO base address via DT_INST_REG_ADDR(0),
      does not rely on the consumer device's reg parameter.